headline: Stanley Black & Decker To Present At The Morgan Stanley 13th Annual Laguna Conference
summary: Stanley Black & Decker (NYSE: SWK) invites investors and the general public to listen to a webcast of a presentation by Pat Hallinan, Executive Vice President and CFO, at Morgan Stanley's 13th Annual Laguna Conference on Thursday, September 11th, 2025 at 1:05 PM PDT (4:05 PM ET).
